{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":683,"text":"It was November 1, 2002,"},{"time":6208,"text":"my first day as a principal,"},{"time":9677,"text":"but hardly my first day\nin the school district of Philadelphia."}]},{"cues":[{"time":15218,"text":"I graduated from\nPhiladelphia public schools,"},{"time":18625,"text":"and I went on to teach\nspecial education for 20 years"},{"time":22792,"text":"in a low-income, low-performing school"},{"time":26167,"text":"in North Philadelphia,"},{"time":28292,"text":"where crime is rampant"},{"time":30333,"text":"and deep poverty is\namong the highest in the nation."}]},{"cues":[{"time":34958,"text":"Shortly after I walked into my new school,"},{"time":38583,"text":"a huge fight broke out among the girls."},{"time":44083,"text":"After things were quickly under control,"},{"time":47500,"text":"I immediately called a meeting"},{"time":50542,"text":"in the school's auditorium"},{"time":52833,"text":"to introduce myself\nas the school's new principal."},{"time":56792,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":60458,"text":"I walked in angry,"},{"time":63154,"text":"a little nervous --"},{"time":64546,"text":"(Laughter) --"},{"time":65708,"text":"but I was determined"},{"time":67792,"text":"to set the tone for my new students."},{"time":71083,"text":"I started listing as forcefully as I could"},{"time":74958,"text":"my expectations for their behavior"},{"time":78125,"text":"and my expectations\nfor what they would learn in school."},{"time":82625,"text":"When, all of a sudden,"},{"time":85042,"text":"a girl way in the back of the auditorium,"},{"time":88750,"text":"she stood up"},{"time":90875,"text":"and she said, \"Miss!"},{"time":93625,"text":"Miss!\""},{"time":95750,"text":"When our eyes locked, she said,"},{"time":100250,"text":"\"Why do you keep calling this a school?"},{"time":104708,"text":"This is not a school.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":108625,"text":"In one outburst,"},{"time":111125,"text":"Ashley had expressed what I felt"},{"time":115167,"text":"and never quite was able to articulate"},{"time":118292,"text":"about my own experience\nwhen I attended a low-performing school"},{"time":122917,"text":"in the same neighborhood,\nmany, many, many years earlier."},{"time":127500,"text":"That school was definitely not a school."}]},{"cues":[{"time":133000,"text":"Fast forwarding a decade later to 2012,"},{"time":139083,"text":"I was entering my third\nlow-performing school as principal."},{"time":144667,"text":"I was to be Strawberry Mansion's\nfourth principal in four years."},{"time":150750,"text":"It was labeled \"low-performing\nand persistently dangerous\""},{"time":155708,"text":"due to its low test scores"},{"time":158625,"text":"and high number of weapons,"},{"time":161375,"text":"drugs, assaults and arrests."},{"time":165833,"text":"Shortly as I approached the door\nof my new school"},{"time":169750,"text":"and attempted to enter,"},{"time":171542,"text":"and found the door locked with chains,"},{"time":175458,"text":"I could hear Ashley's voice in my ears"},{"time":178875,"text":"going, \"Miss! Miss!"},{"time":182833,"text":"This is not a school.\""},{"time":185792,"text":"The halls were dim and dark\nfrom poor lighting."},{"time":189708,"text":"There were tons of piles\nof broken old furniture"},{"time":193042,"text":"and desks in the classrooms,"},{"time":195333,"text":"and there were thousands\nof unused materials and resources."},{"time":200625,"text":"This was not a school."},{"time":204292,"text":"As the year progressed,"},{"time":206750,"text":"I noticed that the classrooms\nwere nearly empty."},{"time":211958,"text":"The students were just scared:"},{"time":214750,"text":"scared to sit in rows in fear\nthat something would happen;"},{"time":219583,"text":"scared because they were often teased\nin the cafeteria for eating free food."},{"time":224792,"text":"They were scared from all the fighting\nand all the bullying."},{"time":229792,"text":"This was not a school."}]},{"cues":[{"time":235375,"text":"And then, there were the teachers,"},{"time":238125,"text":"who were incredibly afraid\nfor their own safety,"},{"time":242833,"text":"so they had low expectations\nfor the students and themselves,"},{"time":248500,"text":"and they were totally\nunaware of their role"},{"time":251833,"text":"in the destruction\nof the school's culture."},{"time":254500,"text":"This was the most troubling of all."},{"time":258791,"text":"You see, Ashley was right,"},{"time":262833,"text":"and not just about her school."},{"time":265667,"text":"For far too many schools,"},{"time":267833,"text":"for kids who live in poverty,"},{"time":269917,"text":"their schools are really\nnot schools at all."},{"time":273583,"text":"But this can change."},{"time":275958,"text":"Let me tell you how it's being done\nat Strawberry Mansion High School."},{"time":282083,"text":"Anybody who's ever worked\nwith me will tell you"},{"time":285917,"text":"I am known for my slogans."},{"time":288583,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":290000,"text":"So today, I am going to use three"},{"time":293554,"text":"that have been paramount\nin our quest for change."}]},{"cues":[{"time":297917,"text":"My first slogan is:"},{"time":300458,"text":"if you're going to lead, lead."},{"time":303750,"text":"I always believed"},{"time":305894,"text":"that what happens in a school\nand what does not happen in a school"},{"time":309792,"text":"is up to the principal."},{"time":311958,"text":"I am the principal,"},{"time":313833,"text":"and having that title required me to lead."},{"time":318125,"text":"I was not going to stay in my office,"},{"time":320846,"text":"I was not going to delegate my work,"},{"time":323691,"text":"and I was not going to be afraid\nto address anything"},{"time":327160,"text":"that was not good for children,"},{"time":329084,"text":"whether that made me liked or not."},{"time":333228,"text":"I am a leader,"},{"time":334965,"text":"so I know I cannot do anything alone."},{"time":338788,"text":"So, I assembled\na top-notch leadership team"},{"time":341475,"text":"who believed in the possibility\nof all the children,"},{"time":344583,"text":"and together, we tackled the small things,"},{"time":348456,"text":"like resetting every single\nlocker combination by hand"},{"time":353083,"text":"so that every student\ncould have a secure locker."},{"time":356583,"text":"We decorated every\nbulletin board in that building"},{"time":360039,"text":"with bright, colorful,\nand positive messages."},{"time":363428,"text":"We took the chains off\nthe front doors of the school."},{"time":366579,"text":"We got the lightbulbs replaced,"},{"time":368698,"text":"and we cleaned\nevery classroom to its core,"},{"time":371878,"text":"recycling every, every textbook\nthat was not needed,"},{"time":376377,"text":"and discarded thousands\nof old materials and furniture."},{"time":380692,"text":"We used two dumpsters per day."}]},{"cues":[{"time":384875,"text":"And, of course, of course,"},{"time":387456,"text":"we tackled the big stuff,"},{"time":389857,"text":"like rehauling the entire school budget"},{"time":393803,"text":"so that we can reallocate funds\nto have more teachers and support staff."},{"time":399733,"text":"We rebuilt the entire\nschool day schedule from scratch"},{"time":405292,"text":"to add a variety of start and end times,"},{"time":409195,"text":"remediation, honors courses,"},{"time":412792,"text":"extracurricular activities,\nand counseling,"},{"time":416416,"text":"all during the school day."},{"time":419717,"text":"All during the school day."},{"time":424217,"text":"We created a deployment plan"},{"time":428473,"text":"that specified where every single\nsupport person and police officer would be"},{"time":434145,"text":"every minute of the day,"},{"time":435573,"text":"and we monitored\nat every second of the day,"},{"time":439500,"text":"and, our best invention ever,"},{"time":442299,"text":"we devised a schoolwide\ndiscipline program"},{"time":445957,"text":"titled \"Non-negotiables.\""},{"time":448137,"text":"It was a behavior system --"},{"time":452368,"text":"designed to promote\npositive behavior at all times."}]},{"cues":[{"time":457131,"text":"The results?"},{"time":459085,"text":"Strawberry Mansion was removed\nfrom the Persistently Dangerous List"},{"time":463237,"text":"our first year after being --"},{"time":465700,"text":"(Applause) --"},{"time":471800,"text":"after being on the Persistently\nDangerous List for five consecutive years."},{"time":476732,"text":"Leaders make the impossible possible."}]},{"cues":[{"time":481939,"text":"That brings me to my second slogan:"},{"time":484865,"text":"So what? Now what?"},{"time":487491,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":488597,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":493483,"text":"When we looked at the data,"},{"time":495718,"text":"and we met with the staff,"},{"time":497812,"text":"there were many excuses"},{"time":499750,"text":"for why Strawberry Mansion was\nlow-performing and persistently dangerous."},{"time":504129,"text":"They said that only 68 percent of the kids\ncome to school on a regular basis,"},{"time":509020,"text":"100 percent of them live in poverty,"},{"time":512587,"text":"only one percent\nof the parents participate,"},{"time":516173,"text":"many of the children"},{"time":517828,"text":"come from incarceration\nand single-parent homes,"},{"time":521400,"text":"39 percent of the students\nhave special needs,"},{"time":525728,"text":"and the state data revealed"},{"time":528695,"text":"that six percent of the students\nwere proficient in algebra,"},{"time":533017,"text":"and 10 were proficient in literature."}]},{"cues":[{"time":538817,"text":"After they got through\ntelling us all the stories"},{"time":542767,"text":"of how awful the conditions\nand the children were,"},{"time":546750,"text":"I looked at them,"},{"time":549162,"text":"and I said, \"So what. Now what?"},{"time":553088,"text":"What are we gonna do about it?\""},{"time":554915,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":560654,"text":"Eliminating excuses at every turn\nbecame my primary responsibility."},{"time":566552,"text":"We addressed every one of those excuses"},{"time":569614,"text":"through a mandatory\nprofessional development,"},{"time":572194,"text":"paving the way for intense focus\non teaching and learning."},{"time":578037,"text":"After many observations,"},{"time":580180,"text":"what we determined was\nthat teachers knew what to teach"},{"time":585462,"text":"but they did not know how to teach"},{"time":588250,"text":"so many children\nwith so many vast abilities."},{"time":591798,"text":"So, we developed a lesson\ndelivery model for instruction"},{"time":596896,"text":"that focused on small group instruction,"},{"time":600660,"text":"making it possible for all the students\nto get their individual needs met"},{"time":605478,"text":"in the classroom."}]},{"cues":[{"time":607170,"text":"The results?"},{"time":609149,"text":"After one year, state data revealed"},{"time":613826,"text":"that our scores have grown\nby 171 percent in Algebra"},{"time":618161,"text":"and 107 percent in literature."},{"time":620806,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":625300,"text":"We have a very long way to go,"},{"time":628049,"text":"a very long way to go,"},{"time":630625,"text":"but we now approach every obstacle\nwith a \"So What. Now What?\" attitude."}]},{"cues":[{"time":638377,"text":"And that brings me\nto my third and final slogan."},{"time":642486,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":644160,"text":"If nobody told you they loved you today,"},{"time":648678,"text":"you remember I do, and I always will."}]},{"cues":[{"time":653079,"text":"My students have problems:"},{"time":655875,"text":"social, emotional and economic problems"},{"time":660448,"text":"you could never imagine."},{"time":663056,"text":"Some of them are parents themselves,"},{"time":665418,"text":"and some are completely alone."},{"time":669375,"text":"If someone asked me my real secret"},{"time":672917,"text":"for how I truly keep\nStrawberry Mansion moving forward,"},{"time":677405,"text":"I would have to say\nthat I love my students"},{"time":680935,"text":"and I believe in their possibilities"},{"time":683427,"text":"unconditionally."},{"time":686000,"text":"When I look at them,"},{"time":688235,"text":"I can only see what they can become,"},{"time":691869,"text":"and that is because I am one of them."},{"time":696542,"text":"I grew up poor in North Philadelphia too."},{"time":700261,"text":"I know what it feels like\nto go to a school that's not a school."},{"time":706184,"text":"I know what it feels like to wonder"},{"time":709458,"text":"if there's ever going to be\nany way out of poverty."},{"time":714092,"text":"But because of my amazing mother,"},{"time":718496,"text":"I got the ability to dream"},{"time":721586,"text":"despite the poverty that surrounded me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":725161,"text":"So --"},{"time":726383,"text":"(Applause) --"},{"time":728855,"text":"if I'm going to push my students"},{"time":733972,"text":"toward their dream\nand their purpose in life,"},{"time":736769,"text":"I've got to get to know who they are."},{"time":740042,"text":"So I have to spend time with them,"},{"time":742918,"text":"so I manage the lunchroom every day."},{"time":745342,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":746655,"text":"And while I'm there,"},{"time":748896,"text":"I talk to them\nabout deeply personal things,"},{"time":753830,"text":"and when it's their birthday,"},{"time":755937,"text":"I sing \"Happy Birthday\""},{"time":757890,"text":"even though I cannot sing at all."},{"time":760060,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":762116,"text":"I often ask them,"},{"time":763864,"text":"\"Why do you want me to sing\nwhen I cannot sing at all?\""},{"time":767821,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":769683,"text":"And they respond by saying,"},{"time":772284,"text":"\"Because we like feeling special.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":776259,"text":"We hold monthly town hall meetings"},{"time":779611,"text":"to listen to their concerns,"},{"time":782565,"text":"to find out what is on their minds."},{"time":786784,"text":"They ask us questions like,\n\"Why do we have to follow rules?\""},{"time":792255,"text":"\"Why are there so many consequences?\""},{"time":795168,"text":"\"Why can't we just do what we want to do?\""},{"time":798159,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":800414,"text":"They ask, and I answer\neach question honestly,"},{"time":804932,"text":"and this exchange in listening\nhelps to clear up any misconceptions."},{"time":811860,"text":"Every moment is a teachable moment."}]},{"cues":[{"time":816965,"text":"My reward,"},{"time":819359,"text":"my reward"},{"time":822759,"text":"for being non-negotiable\nin my rules and consequences"},{"time":827839,"text":"is their earned respect."},{"time":830564,"text":"I insist on it,"},{"time":832878,"text":"and because of this,\nwe can accomplish things together."},{"time":837952,"text":"They are clear about\nmy expectations for them,"},{"time":842000,"text":"and I repeat those expectations\nevery day over the P.A. system."},{"time":847656,"text":"I remind them --"},{"time":849293,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":851533,"text":"I remind them of those core values"},{"time":855190,"text":"of focus, tradition, excellence,"},{"time":860172,"text":"integrity and perseverance,"},{"time":863133,"text":"and I remind them every day"},{"time":865655,"text":"how education can truly\nchange their lives."},{"time":870216,"text":"And I end every announcement the same:"},{"time":873414,"text":"\"If nobody told you they loved you today,"},{"time":877291,"text":"you remember I do,"},{"time":879056,"text":"and I always will.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":882076,"text":"Ashley's words"},{"time":884893,"text":"of \"Miss, Miss,"},{"time":888224,"text":"this is not a school,\""},{"time":891064,"text":"is forever etched in my mind."},{"time":894354,"text":"If we are truly going\nto make real progress"},{"time":899806,"text":"in addressing poverty,"},{"time":901798,"text":"then we have to make sure"},{"time":904442,"text":"that every school\nthat serves children in poverty"},{"time":908655,"text":"is a real school,"},{"time":911284,"text":"a school, a school --"},{"time":913563,"text":"(Applause) --"},{"time":917458,"text":"a school that provides them with knowledge"},{"time":921264,"text":"and mental training\nto navigate the world around them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":926112,"text":"I do not know all the answers,"},{"time":929458,"text":"but what I do know is for those\nof us who are privileged"},{"time":935500,"text":"and have the responsibility of leading\na school that serves children in poverty,"},{"time":941042,"text":"we must truly lead,"},{"time":943292,"text":"and when we are faced\nwith unbelievable challenges,"},{"time":946941,"text":"we must stop and ask ourselves,\n\"So what. Now what?"},{"time":952750,"text":"What are we going to do about it?\""},{"time":956060,"text":"And as we lead,"},{"time":958063,"text":"we must never forget"},{"time":960677,"text":"that every single one of our students"},{"time":963917,"text":"is just a child,"},{"time":965990,"text":"often scared by what the world\ntells them they should be,"},{"time":971797,"text":"and no matter what the rest\nof the world tells them they should be,"},{"time":978139,"text":"we should always provide them with hope,"},{"time":981438,"text":"our undivided attention,"},{"time":984656,"text":"unwavering belief in their potential,"},{"time":987806,"text":"consistent expectations,"},{"time":990303,"text":"and we must tell them often,"},{"time":993117,"text":"if nobody told them they loved them today,"},{"time":996717,"text":"remember we do, and we always will."}]},{"cues":[{"time":999844,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1001081,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1012058,"text":"Thank you, Jesus."}]}]}